Asteroids clone in C++ and SDL

A remake of the classic Asteroids game

Controls
[UP] : Thrust forward in facing direction
[LEFT] : Rotate left
[RIGHT]: Rotate right
[DOWN] : Teleport spaceship
[SPACE] : Shoot
[ESC] : Quit the game

Dependencies

This game requires SDL, SDL_image, and SDL_ttf.


Project tested on ubuntu 18.04

Compilation

make

Execution

./main
